          <taggedValue xmi:id="_uTgGkWnAEfGQnbnMwrHD6w" tag="Description" value="counts the number of blank rows. A blank is a non null textual data that contains only white spaces (or nothing). Note that Oracle does not distinguish between the empty string and the null value"/>
